{"lemma":"نَجِيباتٌ","slug":"نَجِيباتٌ","root":"ن.ج.ب","root_slug":"ن-ج-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ج-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["adj","name","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n39350"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"noble, illustrious, distinguished, whiz"},{"pos":"name","gloss":"a male given name, Najib or Najeeb, feminine equivalent نَجِيبَة (najība)"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/na.d͡ʒiːb/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n39350","headword_ar":"نَجِيبٌ","root":"njb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"generous, noble, liberal,"},{"kind":"text","text":"man; (S, K;) one"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distinguished by rank"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quality, nobility"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eminence, reputation"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"note"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"consideration;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excellent; of great worth in his kind;"},{"kind":"text","text":"one who is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like his father in generosity and actions:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najobN","text_ar":"نَجْبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) [explained as signifying “ liberal, generous ”] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nujabapN","text_ar":"نُجَبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) or you call a man"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"njyb","text_ar":"نجيب"},{"kind":"text","text":"when he is generous, noble, or liberal; but when he is unequalled among his people in generosity, &c., you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qawomihi","text_ar":"قَوْمِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa najabapu","text_ar":"هُوَ نَجَبَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", in measure like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Halamap","text_ar":"حَلَمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (El-'Alam Es-Sakháwee:) [but MF doubts the correctness of this measure; and seems to think that the correct word is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nujabap","text_ar":"نُجَبَة","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":":]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alqawomi","text_ar":"القَوْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hw nujabapu","text_ar":"هو نُجَبَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said of a man when he is the man, among them, who is distinguished by generosity, &c.: (S:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nujabaA='u","text_ar":"نُجَبَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anojaAbN","text_ar":"اَنْجَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nujubN","text_ar":"نُجُبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najiybN","text_ar":"نَجِيبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Excellent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as an epithet applied to any animal; (IAth;) a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"generous, excellent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"camel or horse; one"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of high breed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISd;) a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strong, light, swift,"},{"kind":"text","text":"camel: (TA:) you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAqapN najiybapN","text_ar":"نَاقَةٌ نَجِيبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as well as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nAqp najiybN","text_ar":"ناقة نَجِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najaAy^ibu","text_ar":"نَجَايِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nujubN","text_ar":"نُجُبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najaAy^ibu AlquroA=ni","text_ar":"نَجَايِبُ القُرْا=نِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The most excellent, and the purest, parts of the Kur-án."},{"kind":"text","text":"Of such is the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwrapu AlA^anoEaAm","text_ar":"سُورَةُ الاَنْعَام"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) In like manner, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nawaAjibuhu","text_ar":"نَوَاجِبُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The heart thereof"},{"kind":"text","text":"that has [as it were] no"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najab","text_ar":"نَجَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or bark] upon it: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the best,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"most excellent, thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","K","S"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}